{
  "stem": "21310.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I pretended I didn't understand him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he came right out with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, I think you're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I'm going to protect you, if you agree to be my mistress.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And here I was, you know, a young girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I didn't know now what to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Should I become his mistress, or what?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so I was still stunned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- [LAUGHS] he must have been in his late 50s maybe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he came, and he came at me, and he was smiling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All I can remember is his half-rotten teeth, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw-- and-- and I think up to that point I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, if I should submit, or-- or what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And but when I saw these half-rotten teeth and and that grin, I just slapped him so hard in the face.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I started to cuss in good Polish cuss words.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, you so-in-so, how dare you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Aren't you ashamed?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said-- then I said, if you don't get out of here immediately and leave me alone, I go to your wife-- he had a wife there and about four kids-- and tell her about-- about it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not only that, I said, but I am going to go to the Gestapo, and tell them that you are willing to hide a Jew for some favors.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] He got so scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never had trouble with him anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my-- I told my friend, and they moved out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they realized that he must have you know, got-- got suspicious from once I recommended the family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he probably knew that they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I helped in so far that I gave them the false ID cards.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
